! Palenight Theme for CodeMirror 6

An elegant and juicy material-like theme with purple/blue undertones.

Based on [[Palenight|https://github.com/whizkydee/vscode-palenight-theme]].

!! Variants

* `palenight` - Default
* `palenight-italic` - With italicized keywords

!! Available Theme Classes

| !Class | !Description |
| `cm6-theme-palenight` | Default |
| `cm6-theme-palenight-italic` | Italic keywords |
